          reqtools requesters will be closed when the main window is closed.
        Ę Window positions will be saved in the prefs-file. Also the state
          of the scope (on/off) will be saved.
        Ę Doesn't interfere with serial transfers on slower Amigas anymore.
          Exceptions are MED, TFMX, The Player.
          They use their own way of timing (level 6 here I come).
        Ę Works correctly on both PAL and NTSC.
        Ę Behaves more intelligently with bigger fonts, eh...
        Ę If playingmode is 'Random', Next/Prev will randomize a new
          module instead of what they would normally do.
        Ę Removed a bug in ProTracker's arpeggio.
        Ę Newlook propgadgets on Kickstarts 2.0+.
